    image: "/images/programs/bba-in-sports-management-banner.webp",
    ...buildProgramSectionImages("bba-in-sports-management"),
    description: "The BBA in Sports Management at IAER Kolkata is a career-oriented undergraduate programme designed for students who are passionate about sports and want to build careers in the sports industry, event management, sports marketing, and sports business management.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild Your Career with a Leading Sports Management College in Kolkata\nThe BBA in Sports Management at IAER Kolkata is a career-oriented undergraduate programme designed for students who are passionate about sports and want to build careers in the sports industry, event management, sports marketing, and sports business management.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best sports management colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong blend of business management education and sports industry training. Students searching for a top BBA sports management college in Kolkata or a sports management course after 12th will find this programme aligned with modern industry requirements.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Sports Management Training\nAs a top sports management course in Kolkata, the programme focuses on developing skills required to manage sports organizations, events, teams, and athletes.\nStudents are trained in:\n Sports Management & Administration\n Sports Marketing & Branding\n Event & Tournament Management\n Sponsorship & Sports Business\n Sports Analytics & Performance Management\n Media & Broadcasting in Sports\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n sports management courses after 12th\n sports business management degree in Kolkata\n career in sports management India\n\nPractical Learning & Sports Industry Exposure\nIAER focuses on hands-on learning through sports events, live projects, and industry exposure.\nStudents gain practical experience in:\n Organizing Sports Events & Tournaments\n Managing Teams & Athletes\n Sponsorship & Branding Activities\n Sports Promotion & Media Coordination\nThis ensures students are job-ready for careers in the sports industry and event management sector.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned sports management curriculum\n Strong foundation in business + sports management\n Practical exposure through sports events and projects\n Internship opportunities in sports organizations\n Personality development and communication training\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MBA / PGDM in Sports Management\n\nInternship Opportunities in Sports Industry\nIAER provides structured internships to ensure students gain real-world experience in the sports ecosystem.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n Sports Academies & Clubs\n Event Management Companies\n Sports Marketing Agencies\n Fitness & Training Organizations\n Media & Broadcasting Firms\nInternship Roles Include:\n Sports Event Management Intern\n Sports Marketing Intern\n Team Management Intern\n Sponsorship & Branding Intern\n Operations Intern\nThese internships help students build strong foundations for sports management careers in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in sports organizations, event companies, and corporate sectors.\nStudents are supported through:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Skill Development Sessions\n Industry Interaction & Sports Exposure\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore exciting roles, including some of the best sports management jobs in Kolkata.\n\nSports Careers:\n Sports Manager\n Team Manager\n Sports Event Coordinator\n Sports Marketing Executive\n\nEvent & Media Roles:\n Event Manager\n Sports Promotion Executive\n Media & Broadcasting Coordinator\n\nBusiness Roles:\n Sponsorship Manager\n Business Development Executive (Sports Industry)\n\nGrowing Demand in Sports Industry\nThe sports industry in India is growing rapidly with increasing investment in leagues, tournaments, and sports infrastructure. This has created strong demand for professionals from top sports management colleges in Kolkata and across India.\nCareer opportunities exist in:\n Sports Leagues & Teams\n Event Management Companies\n Sports Marketing Agencies\n Fitness & Training Industry\n Media & Broadcasting\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BBA in Sports Management?\nIt is a professional undergraduate programme that combines business management with sports industry knowledge and event management skills.\n\nWhich is the best sports management college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best sports management colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs sports management a good career option?\nYes, it offers exciting career opportunities in sports events, marketing, team management, and media.\n\nWhat are the best sports management jobs in Kolkata?\nTop roles include sports manager, event coordinator, sports marketing executive, and team manager.\n\nCan I do sports management after 12th?\nYes, students from any stream can apply for BBA Sports Management programmes.\n\nEnquire Now – BBA Sports Management Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\n\nTurn Your Passion for Sports into a Career\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
