    id: "bba-business-analytics-kolkata",
    code: "BBA-BA",
    title: "BBA in Business Analytics – IAER Kolkata",
    subtitle: "Undergraduate Degree I MAKAUT Affiliated I AICTE Approved",
    image: "/images/programs/bba-in-business-analytics-banner.webp",
    ...buildProgramSectionImages("bba-in-business-analytics"),
    description: "The BBA in Business Analytics at IAER Kolkata is a future-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in data analytics, business intelligence, and decision-making roles.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹5,04,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild a Data-Driven Career with a Leading Business Analytics College in Kolkata\nThe BBA in Business Analytics at IAER Kolkata is a future-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in data analytics, business intelligence, and decision-making roles.\nIAER is recognized as one of the best business analytics colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong blend of management education and data analytics training. Students looking for a top BBA business analytics college in Kolkata or a job-oriented analytics course after 12th will find this programme aligned with industry demand.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Business Analytics Training\nAs a top business analytics course in Kolkata, the programme equips students with both business knowledge and analytical skills required in today’s digital economy.\nStudents are trained in:\n Data Analysis & Visualization\n Business Intelligence & Reporting\n Excel, SQL & Data Tools\n Marketing Analytics\n Financial Analytics\n Data-Driven Decision Making\nThis programme is ideal for students searching for business analytics courses after 12th or a data analytics degree in Kolkata.\n\nPractical Learning & Analytics Skill Development\nIAER focuses on hands-on learning and real-world application of analytics concepts. Students work on case studies, live projects, and datasets to build practical expertise.\nKey learning areas include:\n Dashboard Creation & Data Visualization\n Predictive Analytics Basics\n Business Problem Solving Using Data\n Digital Strategy & Analytics\nThis ensures students are job-ready for roles in data analytics, business analytics, and digital business environments.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned business analytics curriculum\n Strong foundation in business + data analytics\n Practical training using real datasets\n Internship opportunities in analytics and corporate sectors\n Exposure to modern analytics tools\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MBA / PGDM in Business Analytics or Data Science\n\nInternship Opportunities with Industry Exposure\nIAER provides structured internship opportunities to ensure students gain real-world experience before graduation. Students get exposure to corporate environments, analytics projects, and business operations.\nInternships are offered with:\n Corporate Companies\n IT & Analytics Firms\n Digital Marketing Agencies\n Financial & Consulting Firms\n Startups & Business Organizations\nInternship Roles Include:\n Business Analytics Intern\n Data Analyst Intern\n Marketing Analytics Intern\n Financial Data Intern\n MIS & Reporting Intern\nThese internships help students develop practical skills and prepare for high-demand analytics jobs in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Support\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure opportunities in leading companies across industries. With a strong focus on employability, IAER supports students through:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Skill Development Sessions\n Industry Interaction & Networking Opportunities\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nStudents completing this programme become eligible for roles in top sectors such as IT, consulting, finance, and digital business.\nGraduates can explore some of the best business analytics jobs in Kolkata, including:\n\nAnalytics Careers:\n Business Analyst\n Data Analyst\n MIS Executive\n Reporting Analyst\n\nCorporate Roles:\n Marketing Analyst\n Financial Analyst\n Operations Analyst\n\nDigital & Tech Roles:\n Digital Marketing Analyst\n CRM Analyst\n E-commerce Analyst\n\nGrowing Demand for Business Analytics Professionals\nWith the rapid growth of digital transformation, companies are increasingly relying on data for decision-making. This has created high demand for professionals from top business analytics colleges in Kolkata and across India.\nCareer opportunities exist in:\n IT & Technology Companies\n E-commerce & Startups\n Banking & Financial Institutions\n Consulting & Research Firms\n Digital Marketing Agencies\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BBA in Business Analytics?\nIt is a professional undergraduate programme that combines business management with data analytics, tools, and decision-making techniques.\n\nWhich is the best business analytics college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best business analytics colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs Business Analytics a good career option?\nYes, it offers excellent career opportunities in data analytics, consulting, finance, and digital business.\n\nWhat are the best business analytics jobs in Kolkata?\nTop roles include business analyst, data analyst, marketing analyst, and MIS executive.\n\nCan I do business analytics after 12th?\nYes, students from any stream can apply for BBA Business Analytics programmes.\n\nEnquire Now – BBA Business Analytics Admission Open 2026\n\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nStart Your Career in Data & Analytics\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
