    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹5,04,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nStudy at a Leading Global Business College in Kolkata\nThe BBA in Global Business at IAER Kolkata is designed for students who aspire to build careers in international business, global trade, multinational companies, and cross-border management roles.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best global business colleges in Kolkata, offering a curriculum that blends business management with international exposure and global industry practices.\nStudents looking for a top BBA global business college in Kolkata or an international business course after 12th will find this programme highly relevant.\n\nInternational Exposure with Global University Collaborations\nOne of the key highlights of this programme is its strong focus on global learning through international immersion programmes and academic collaborations.\nIAER offers opportunities for students to gain exposure through partnerships with reputed international institutions such as:\n University of Sunderland, United Kingdom\n University of South Wales , United Kingdom\n Lincoln University College , Malaysia\n SEGi University , Malaysia\n FPT University , Vietnam\n INTI International University , Malaysia\n Management Development Institute of Singapore , SIngapore\nThrough these collaborations, students can benefit from:\n International Immersion Programmes\n Global Classroom Exposure\n Cross-Cultural Learning\n Industry Visits & Workshops\n Networking with International Faculty\nThis makes IAER one of the top colleges for global business studies in Kolkata with international exposure.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Global Business Training\nAs a top global business course in Kolkata, this programme focuses on developing skills required to operate in a global business environment.\nStudents are trained in:\n International Business Management\n Global Marketing & Trade\n Export-Import Management\n Cross-Cultural Communication\n International Finance\n Business Strategy & Leadership\nThis programme is ideal for students searching for:\n international business course after 12th\n global business degree in Kolkata\n study abroad exposure with BBA\n\nInternship Opportunities & Global Exposure\nIAER ensures students gain real-world experience through internships in both domestic and international business environments.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n Multinational Companies (MNCs)\n Export-Import Firms\n Logistics & Supply Chain Companies\n International Trade Organizations\n Corporate & Consulting Firms\nInternship Roles Include:\n International Business Intern\n Export-Import Executive Intern\n Global Marketing Intern\n Business Development Intern\n Operations & Supply Chain Intern\nThese internships prepare students for global business careers and international job roles.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER provides dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in leading national and multinational companies.\nWith strong industry connections and career support, students are trained for high-growth roles in global business sectors.\nCareer Opportunities Include:\n International Business Executive\n Export-Import Manager\n Global Marketing Executive\n Business Development Executive\n Supply Chain & Logistics Executive\n Management Trainee (MNCs)\nStudents can explore opportunities in:\n Multinational Corporations\n International Trade Companies\n Consulting Firms\n E-commerce & Global Businesses\nGraduates are prepared for high-paying global business jobs in India and abroad.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Global business-focused curriculum\n International immersion programmes\n Collaboration with foreign universities\n Strong foundation in business management\n Internship opportunities in global companies\n Personality development & communication training\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MBA / PGDM in International Business\n\nCareer Scope in Global Business\nWith globalization and expansion of international trade, the demand for professionals with global business knowledge is rapidly increasing.\nGraduates from top global business colleges in Kolkata can build careers in:\n International Trade & Export Houses\n Multinational Companies\n Global Consulting Firms\n Logistics & Supply Chain Industry\n International Marketing & Sales\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BBA in Global Business?\nIt is a professional undergraduate programme focused on international business, global trade, and cross-border management.\n\nWhich is the best global business college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best global business colleges in Kolkata, offering international exposure and industry-oriented training.\n\nDoes this course offer international exposure?\nYes, IAER provides international immersion programmes through collaborations with global universities.\n\nWhat are the career opportunities after BBA Global Business?\nStudents can work in multinational companies, export-import firms, global marketing, and international business roles.\n\nCan I study abroad during this course?\nYes, students can participate in international immersion programmes and global exposure initiatives.\n\nEnquire Now – BBA Global Business Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nInternational Exposure Opportunities\nScholarship Available\nBuild Your Global Career\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
