    description: "The BCA course at IAER Kolkata is a career-oriented undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in the IT industry, software development, data analytics, and digital technology sectors.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild Your Career with a Top BCA College in Kolkata\nThe BCA course at IAER Kolkata is a career-oriented undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in the IT industry, software development, data analytics, and digital technology sectors.\nIAER is recognized as one of the best BCA colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong foundation in programming, software development, and computer applications. Students searching for a top BCA college in Kolkata or a job-oriented IT course after 12th will find this programme highly relevant.\n\nIndustry-Oriented IT & Software Development Training\nAs a top BCA course in Kolkata, this programme focuses on building both technical and practical skills required in the IT industry.\nStudents are trained in:\n Programming Languages (C, C++, Java, Python)\n Web Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)\n Database Management (SQL)\n Software Development & Testing\n Operating Systems & Computer Networks\n Basics of Data Science & Analytics\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n computer application course after 12th\n IT courses in Kolkata with placement\n best BCA course in Kolkata\n\nPractical Learning & Technical Skill Development\nIAER emphasizes hands-on learning through projects, coding practice, and real-world problem-solving.\nStudents gain practical experience in:\n Software Development Projects\n Website & Application Development\n Database Design & Management\n Debugging & Testing\nThis ensures students are job-ready for roles in the IT and software industry.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned BCA curriculum\n Strong foundation in programming and software development\n Practical learning through projects and coding labs\n Internship opportunities in IT companies\n Exposure to modern technologies\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MCA / MBA / Data Science programs\n\nInternship Opportunities in IT Industry\nIAER provides structured internship opportunities to ensure students gain real-world exposure in the IT sector.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n IT Companies & Software Firms\n Web Development Agencies\n Startups & Tech Companies\n Digital & IT Service Providers\nInternship Roles Include:\n Software Developer Intern\n Web Developer Intern\n Data Analyst Intern\n Technical Support Intern\n QA & Testing Intern\nThese internships help students build strong foundations for IT careers in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in leading IT companies and tech-driven organizations.\nStudents receive:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Technical Training\n Industry Interaction & Project Exposure\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore a wide range of roles, including some of the best BCA jobs in Kolkata.\n\nIT Careers:\n Software Developer\n Web Developer\n Application Developer\n Technical Support Engineer\n\nData & Analytics Roles:\n Data Analyst\n MIS Executive\n\nDigital Roles:\n Digital Marketing Executive\n SEO Analyst\n\nCareer Scope After BCA\nThe demand for IT professionals is growing rapidly due to digital transformation across industries.\nGraduates from top BCA colleges in Kolkata are highly in demand in:\n IT & Software Companies\n Startups & Tech Firms\n Banking & Financial Technology (FinTech)\n E-commerce Companies\n Digital Service Industry\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BCA?\nBCA (Bachelor of Computer Applications) is a professional undergraduate degree focused on computer applications, programming, and IT skills.\n\nWhich is the best BCA college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best BCA colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs BCA a good career option?\nYes, it offers excellent career opportunities in software development, IT services, and data analytics.\n\nWhat are the best jobs after BCA?\nPopular roles include software developer, web developer, data analyst, and IT support engineer.\n\nCan I do BCA after 12th?\nYes, students from any stream can apply for BCA programmes.\n\nEnquire Now – BCA Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nStart Your Career in IT & Technology\n\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
