    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild a Future-Ready Career with a Top AI & Machine Learning College in Kolkata\nThe BCA in Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning at IAER Kolkata is a future-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in AI, machine learning, data science, and emerging technologies.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best AI & ML colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong foundation in programming, artificial intelligence, and data-driven technologies. Students searching for a top BCA AI ML college in Kolkata or an AI course after 12th will find this programme highly aligned with industry demand.\n\nIndustry-Oriented AI & Machine Learning Training\nAs a top artificial intelligence course in Kolkata, this programme combines core computer science with advanced AI and machine learning concepts.\nStudents are trained in:\n Programming (Python, Java, C++)\n Machine Learning Algorithms\n Artificial Intelligence Fundamentals\n Data Science & Analytics\n Deep Learning Basics\n Natural Language Processing (NLP)\n Computer Vision\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n artificial intelligence course after 12th\n machine learning course in Kolkata\n data science and AI degree in Kolkata\n\nPractical Learning & AI Skill Development\nIAER focuses on hands-on training through real-world projects and datasets to build practical expertise in AI technologies.\nStudents gain experience in:\n Building Machine Learning Models\n Data Analysis & Visualization\n AI-based Application Development\n Working with Real Datasets\nThis ensures students are job-ready for careers in AI, ML, and data science domains.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned AI & ML curriculum\n Strong foundation in programming + data science\n Practical learning through projects and case studies\n Internship opportunities in AI and tech companies\n Exposure to modern tools and technologies\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MCA / MBA / Data Science & AI specializations\n\nInternship Opportunities in AI & Tech Industry\nIAER provides structured internships to ensure students gain real-world exposure in AI-driven environments.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n IT & Software Companies\n AI & Data Science Firms\n Startups & Tech Companies\n Analytics & Research Organizations\nInternship Roles Include:\n Machine Learning Intern\n Data Analyst Intern\n AI Developer Intern\n Python Developer Intern\n Data Science Intern\nThese internships help students build strong foundations for AI and machine learning careers in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in top technology companies and data-driven organizations.\nStudents are supported through:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Technical Training\n Live Project Experience\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore high-demand roles, including some of the best AI jobs in Kolkata.\n\nAI & ML Careers:\n Machine Learning Engineer\n AI Developer\n Data Scientist\n Data Analyst\n\nIT & Development Roles:\n Python Developer\n Software Developer\n Application Developer\n\nAnalytics Roles:\n Business Intelligence Analyst\n Data Analyst\n\nFuture Scope of AI & Machine Learning\nArtificial Intelligence and Machine Learning are among the fastest-growing fields globally. Companies across industries are adopting AI-driven solutions, creating massive demand for skilled professionals.\nGraduates from top AI colleges in Kolkata can build careers in:\n IT & Software Companies\n Data Science & Analytics Firms\n Startups & Tech Companies\n Banking & FinTech\n E-commerce & Digital Platforms\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BCA in AI & ML?\nIt is a professional undergraduate programme focused on artificial intelligence, machine learning, and data science technologies.\n\nWhich is the best AI college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best AI & ML colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs AI & Machine Learning a good career option?\nYes, it offers high-paying and future-ready career opportunities in technology and data-driven industries.\n\nWhat are the best AI jobs in Kolkata?\nTop roles include machine learning engineer, data scientist, AI developer, and data analyst.\n\nCan I do AI after 12th?\nYes, students from any stream can apply for BCA AI & ML programmes.\n\nEnquire Now – BCA AI & ML Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nStart Your Career in Artificial Intelligence\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
