    description: "The BCA in Data Science & Cyber Security at IAER Kolkata is a future-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in data science, cyber security, ethical hacking, and IT security domains.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild a Future-Ready Career with a Top Data Science & Cyber Security College in Kolkata\nThe BCA in Data Science & Cyber Security at IAER Kolkata is a future-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in data science, cyber security, ethical hacking, and IT security domains.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best data science and cyber security colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong foundation in programming, analytics, and cyber security technologies. Students searching for a top BCA data science college in Kolkata or a cyber security course after 12th will find this programme highly aligned with industry demand.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Training in Data Science & Cyber Security\nAs a top data science and cyber security course in Kolkata, this programme provides dual specialization in two of the most in-demand tech domains.\nStudents are trained in:\nData Science:\n Data Analysis & Visualization\n Python for Data Science\n Machine Learning Basics\n Data Mining & Statistics\n Business Intelligence\nCyber Security:\n Network Security\n Ethical Hacking\n Cyber Laws & Digital Forensics\n Information Security Management\n Cloud & Application Security\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n data science course after 12th\n cyber security course in Kolkata\n IT security and data analytics degree\n\nPractical Learning & Technology Skill Development\nIAER emphasizes hands-on training to ensure students gain real-world expertise in both analytics and cyber security domains.\nStudents gain experience in:\n Working with real datasets and analytics tools\n Building data-driven models\n Cyber security simulations and testing\n Ethical hacking fundamentals\nThis ensures students are job-ready for roles in data science, cyber security, and IT sectors.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Dual specialization in data science and cyber security\n Industry-aligned curriculum with latest technologies\n Strong foundation in programming and analytics\n Practical learning through projects and labs\n Internship opportunities in IT and security domains\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MCA / MBA / Data Science / Cyber Security specializations\n\nInternship Opportunities in IT & Security Industry\nIAER provides structured internship opportunities to ensure students gain real-world exposure in high-demand tech domains.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n IT & Software Companies\n Cyber Security Firms\n Data Analytics Companies\n Startups & Tech Organizations\n Digital Security & Consulting Firms\nInternship Roles Include:\n Data Analyst Intern\n Cyber Security Intern\n Ethical Hacking Intern\n SOC (Security Operations Centre) Intern\n IT Support & Security Intern\nThese internships prepare students for high-demand tech careers in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in top IT companies, analytics firms, and cyber security organizations.\n\nStudents receive:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Technical Training\n Live Projects & Practical Exposure\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore high-growth roles, including some of the best data science and cyber security jobs in Kolkata.\n\nData Science Careers:\n Data Analyst\n Data Scientist\n Business Intelligence Analyst\n\nCyber Security Careers:\n Cyber Security Analyst\n Ethical Hacker\n Network Security Engineer\n SOC Analyst\n\nIT & Tech Roles:\n Python Developer\n Software Developer\n IT Security Executive\n\nFuture Scope of Data Science & Cyber Security\nData and security are two of the fastest-growing fields globally. With increasing digital transformation and cyber threats, companies are actively hiring skilled professionals.\nGraduates from top data science and cyber security colleges in Kolkata can build careers in:\n IT & Software Companies\n Cyber Security Firms\n Banking & FinTech\n E-commerce Platforms\n Government & Defense Sectors\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BCA in Data Science & Cyber Security?\nIt is a professional undergraduate programme combining data analytics, machine learning basics, and cyber security technologies.\n\nWhich is the best data science and cyber security college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best data science and cyber security colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs data science and cyber security a good career option?\nYes, both fields offer high-paying and future-proof career opportunities.\n\nWhat are the best jobs in data science and cyber security?\nTop roles include data analyst, data scientist, cyber security analyst, ethical hacker, and SOC analyst.\n\nCan I do cyber security after 12th?\nYes, students from any stream can apply for BCA Data Science & Cyber Security programmes.\n\nEnquire Now – BCA DSCS Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nStart Your Career in Data & Cyber Security\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
