    description: "The B.Sc. in Cyber Security at IAER Kolkata is a career-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in cyber security, ethical hacking, network security, and information security.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream ) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild a Future-Proof Career with a Top Cyber Security College in Kolkata\nThe B.Sc. in Cyber Security at IAER Kolkata is a career-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to build careers in cyber security, ethical hacking, network security, and information security.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best cyber security colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong foundation in IT security, ethical hacking, and digital protection technologies.\nStudents searching for:\n cyber security course in Kolkata after 12th\n ethical hacking course with degree\n IT security degree in Kolkata with placement\nwill find this programme highly aligned with industry demand.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Cyber Security Training\nAs a top cyber security course in Kolkata, the programme focuses on protecting systems, networks, and data from cyber threats.\nStudents are trained in:\n Ethical Hacking & Penetration Testing\n Network Security\n Cyber Laws & Digital Forensics\n Information Security Management\n Cryptography Basics\n Cloud & Application Security\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n cyber security course after 12th\n ethical hacking course in Kolkata\n information security degree in India\n\nHands-On Learning & Cyber Security Labs\nIAER emphasizes practical training through real-world cyber security simulations and labs.\nStudents gain experience in:\n Identifying Security Vulnerabilities\n Ethical Hacking Techniques\n Network Monitoring & Protection\n Security Testing & Risk Assessment\nThis ensures students are job-ready for cyber security and IT security careers.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned cyber security curriculum\n Strong foundation in ethical hacking and network security\n Practical training through labs and simulations\n Internship opportunities in IT and security companies\n Exposure to modern cyber security tools\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to higher studies (M.Sc. Cyber Security / IT Security)\n\nInternship Opportunities in Cyber Security Industry\nIAER provides structured internships to ensure students gain real-world exposure in IT security domains.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n IT & Software Companies\n Cyber Security Firms\n Network & Security Organizations\n Startups & Tech Companies\nInternship Roles Include:\n Cyber Security Intern\n Ethical Hacking Intern\n Network Security Intern\n SOC (Security Operations Center) Intern\nThese internships help students build strong foundations for cyber security careers in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in top IT and security companies.\nStudents receive:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Technical Training\n Live Project Experience\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore some of the best cyber security jobs in Kolkata.\n\nCyber Security Careers:\n Cyber Security Analyst\n Ethical Hacker\n Network Security Engineer\n SOC Analyst\n\nIT Roles:\n System Administrator\n IT Security Executive\n Security Consultant\n\nFuture Scope of Cyber Security\nWith increasing cyber threats and digital transformation, cyber security is one of the fastest-growing and highest-paying career fields globally.\nStudents completing this BSc Cyber Security course in Kolkata can build careers in:\n IT & Software Companies\n Cyber Security Firms\n Banking & Financial Sector\n Government & Defense Organizations\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is B.Sc. in Cyber Security?\nIt is an undergraduate degree focused on protecting digital systems, networks, and data from cyber threats.\n\nWhich is the best cyber security college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best cyber security colleges in Kolkata, offering practical training and placement support.\n\nIs cyber security a good career option?\nYes, it offers high salary opportunities and strong demand globally.\n\nWhat are the best jobs after cyber security degree?\nPopular roles include cyber security analyst, ethical hacker, and network security engineer.\n\nCan I do cyber security after 12th?\nYes, students from any stream can apply.\n\nEnquire Now – B.Sc. Cyber Security Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nStart Your Career in Cyber Security\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
