    id: "bmlt-medical-lab-technology-kolkata",
    code: "BMLT",
    widgetId: "5f74e92b4f492e8e612fc2ca21f5bdd0",
    title: "BMLT – Bachelor of Medical Laboratory Technology – IAER Kolkata",
    subtitle: "Undergraduate Degree I MAKAUT Affiliated I AICTE Approved",
    image: "/images/programs/bsc-in-medical-laboratory-technology-bmlt-banner.webp",
    ...buildProgramSectionImages("bsc-in-medical-laboratory-technology-bmlt"),
    description: "The BMLT / B.Sc. in Medical Laboratory Technology at IAER Kolkata is a career-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to work in the healthcare, diagnostic, and laboratory science sector.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (Science Stream with Biology preferred) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild a Career with a Leading Medical Laboratory Technology College in Kolkata\nThe BMLT / B.Sc. in Medical Laboratory Technology at IAER Kolkata is a career-focused undergraduate programme designed for students who want to work in the healthcare, diagnostic, and laboratory science sector.\nIAER is recognized as one of the best medical laboratory technology colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong foundation in clinical diagnostics, pathology, and laboratory techniques. Students searching for a top BMLT college in Kolkata or a paramedical course after 12th will find this programme highly aligned with healthcare industry demand.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Medical Laboratory Training\nAs a top medical lab technology course in Kolkata, this programme equips students with the knowledge and practical skills required for diagnostic and laboratory roles in healthcare.\nStudents are trained in:\n Clinical Biochemistry\n Microbiology & Immunology\n Hematology\n Pathology & Histopathology\n Blood Banking & Transfusion Science\n Diagnostic Techniques & Laboratory Equipment\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n medical laboratory technology course after 12th\n paramedical courses in Kolkata with placement\n healthcare diagnostic course in India\n\nPractical Training & Laboratory Exposure\nIAER emphasizes hands-on training through laboratory sessions and clinical exposure.\nStudents gain practical experience in:\n Handling Diagnostic Equipment\n Sample Collection & Testing\n Blood Analysis & Clinical Testing\n Laboratory Safety & Protocols\nThis ensures students are job-ready for roles in hospitals, diagnostic labs, and healthcare centers.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned BMLT curriculum\n Strong foundation in medical diagnostics and laboratory science\n Practical lab training and clinical exposure\n Internship opportunities in hospitals and diagnostic labs\n Exposure to modern diagnostic technologies\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to higher studies (M.Sc. MLT / Healthcare specialization)\n\nInternship Opportunities in Hospitals & Diagnostic Labs\nIAER provides structured internships to ensure students gain real-world clinical experience.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n Hospitals & Multi-Speciality Clinics\n Diagnostic Laboratories\n Pathology Labs\n Healthcare Centers\nInternship Roles Include:\n Lab Technician Intern\n Pathology Lab Intern\n Blood Bank Assistant Intern\n Diagnostic Lab Intern\n Clinical Lab Assistant\nThese internships help students build strong foundations for medical laboratory careers in India.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in hospitals, diagnostic labs, and healthcare organizations.\nStudents receive:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Skill Development\n Hospital & Lab Exposure\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore a wide range of roles, including some of the best medical lab jobs in Kolkata.\n\nHealthcare Careers:\n Medical Laboratory Technician\n Lab Technologist\n Pathology Lab Technician\n Blood Bank Technician\n\nHospital Roles:\n Clinical Lab Executive\n Diagnostic Lab Assistant\n Healthcare Technician\n\nAdvanced Roles:\n Research Lab Assistant\n Quality Control Technician\n\nGrowing Demand for Medical Laboratory Professionals\nThe healthcare sector is expanding rapidly, increasing the demand for skilled diagnostic professionals.\nGraduates from top BMLT colleges in Kolkata are highly in demand in:\n Hospitals & Healthcare Chains\n Diagnostic & Pathology Labs\n Research Laboratories\n Public Health Organizations\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is BMLT?\nBMLT (Bachelor in Medical Laboratory Technology) is a professional undergraduate programme focused on laboratory diagnostics and clinical testing.\n\nWhich is the best BMLT college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best medical laboratory technology colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs medical lab technology a good career option?\nYes, it offers stable and high-demand career opportunities in hospitals and diagnostic centers.\n\nWhat are the best jobs after BMLT?\nPopular roles include lab technician, pathology technician, blood bank technician, and clinical lab technologist.\n\nCan I do BMLT after 12th?\nYes, students from the science stream (preferably with Biology) can apply.\n\nEnquire Now – BMLT Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nStart Your Career in Healthcare & Diagnostics\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
