    id: "bsc-hospitality-hotel-management-kolkata",
    code: "BSCHHA",
    title: "B.Sc. in Hospitality & Hotel Administration (Hotel Management) – IAER Kolkata",
    subtitle: "Undergraduate Degree I MAKAUT Affiliated I AICTE Approved",
    image: "/images/programs/bba-in-hotel-hospitality-administration-banner.webp",
    ...buildProgramSectionImages("bba-in-hotel-hospitality-administration"),
    description: "The B.Sc. in Hospitality & Hotel Administration at IAER Kolkata is a career-focused programme designed for students who want to build careers in the hospitality, hotel, tourism, and service industries.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n4 Years Undergraduate Degree Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nStudents who have completed 10+2 (any stream) from a recognized board are eligible to apply. Students appearing for Class 12 examinations can also apply.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹4,12,000.\nScholarship : Avail ₹ 50,000 Scholarship , Last Date to apply 31 st May 2026.\n\nBuild Your Career with a Leading Hotel Management College in Kolkata\nThe B.Sc. in Hospitality & Hotel Administration at IAER Kolkata is a career-focused programme designed for students who want to build careers in the hospitality, hotel, tourism, and service industries.\nIAER is recognized as one of the best hotel management colleges in Kolkata, offering a strong blend of practical training, industry exposure, and business management education. Students often compare institutions like Institute of Hotel Management, International Institute of Hotel Management, and Guru Nanak Institute of Hotel Management while searching for the top hotel management colleges in Kolkata, and IAER stands out with its career-focused approach and affordable structure.\n\nIndustry-Oriented Hospitality & Hotel Management Training\nAs a top hospitality management course in Kolkata, the programme equips students with the skills required to manage hotels, resorts, restaurants, and service operations.\nStudents are trained in:\n Front Office Operations\n Food & Beverage Service\n Housekeeping Management\n Hotel Operations & Administration\n Hospitality Marketing & Sales\n Event & Tourism Management\nThis programme is ideal for students searching for:\n hotel management course after 12th\n best hotel management colleges like IHM, IIHM, or GNIHM alternatives\n hospitality management degree in Kolkata\n\nPractical Training & Service Industry Exposure\nIAER emphasizes hands-on learning through practical training, simulations, and real-world exposure.\nStudents gain experience in:\n Hotel Operations & Guest Services\n Restaurant & Food Service Management\n Event Planning & Coordination\n Customer Experience Management\nThis ensures students are job-ready for roles in hotels, hospitality chains, and tourism sector.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned hospitality and hotel management curriculum\n Strong foundation in service and business management\n Practical training in hotel operations and service delivery\n Internship opportunities in hotels and hospitality brands\n Personality development and grooming training\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n Pathway to MBA / PGDM in Hospitality or Tourism\n\nInternship Opportunities in Hospitality Industry\nIAER provides structured internships to ensure students gain real-world experience in the hospitality sector.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n Hotels & Resorts\n Restaurant Chains\n Event Management Companies\n Travel & Tourism Organizations\n Cruise & Hospitality Services\nInternship Roles Include:\n Hotel Operations Intern\n Front Office Intern\n Food & Beverage Service Intern\n Housekeeping Intern\n Event Management Intern\nThese internships help students build strong foundations for hospitality careers in India and abroad.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in leading hospitality brands and service organizations.\nStudents receive:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Personality Development\n Industry Interaction & Hotel Exposure\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore exciting roles, including some of the best hotel management jobs in Kolkata.\n\nHospitality Careers:\n Hotel Manager\n Front Office Executive\n Guest Relations Executive\n Food & Beverage Executive\n\nService & Operations Roles:\n Restaurant Manager\n Housekeeping Manager\n Event Coordinator\n\nGlobal Opportunities:\n Cruise Line Staff\n International Hotel Chains\n Tourism & Travel Industry\n\nGlobal Scope in Hospitality Industry\nThe hospitality industry is one of the fastest-growing sectors globally, offering career opportunities in India and abroad.\nStudents comparing institutes like Institute of Hotel Management, International Institute of Hotel Management, or Guru Nanak Institute of Hotel Management will find IAER a strong alternative due to its practical exposure, placement support, and affordability.\nCareer opportunities exist in:\n Hotels & Resorts\n Airlines & Cruise Industry\n Tourism & Travel Companies\n Event & Luxury Service Industry\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhich is the best hotel management college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best hotel management colleges in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training, internships, and placement support.\n\nHow is IAER different from IHM, IIHM, or GNIHM?\nIAER focuses on practical training, industry exposure, and affordability, making it a strong alternative to institutions like Institute of Hotel Management, International Institute of Hotel Management, and Guru Nanak Institute of Hotel Management.\n\nIs hotel management a good career option?\nYes, it offers exciting career opportunities in hotels, tourism, airlines, and global hospitality sectors.\n\nWhat are the best jobs after hotel management?\nPopular roles include hotel manager, front office executive, food & beverage executive, and event manager.\n\nEnquire Now – B.Sc. Hospitality Admission Open 2026\n\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship Opportunities Available\nBuild Your Career in Hospitality\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
