    subtitle: "Postgraduate Degree | MAKAUT-Affiliated | UGC-Recognised",
    image: "/images/programs/MBA-Global.webp",
    ...buildProgramSectionImages("master-of-business-administration-mba"),
    description: "The MBA programme at IAER Kolkata is designed for students who want to build successful careers in business management, corporate leadership, and high-growth industries.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n2 Years Full-Time Postgraduate Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\nGraduates from any recognized university (any stream) are eligible to apply. Final-year students can also apply for MBA admission in Kolkata 2026.\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee : ₹5,95,000. ₹5,45,000\n\nBest MBA College in Kolkata for Career & Placement\nThe MBA programme at IAER Kolkata is designed for students who want to build successful careers in business management, corporate leadership, and high-growth industries.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best MBA colleges in Kolkata, offering a perfect combination of industry-oriented curriculum, practical training, and placement support. Students searching for:\n MBA admission Kolkata\n top MBA colleges in Kolkata\n MBA colleges in Kolkata with placement\nwill find this programme highly aligned with industry requirements.\nMany students compare MBA options from institutions like EIILM, BIBS, URM, Unitedworld School of Business, Globsyn Business School, Praxis Business School, and Techno India University. IAER stands out as a top MBA college in Kolkata with affordable fees and strong placement assistance.\n\nIndustry-Oriented MBA Specializations in Kolkata\nAs a top MBA course in Kolkata, IAER offers specialization-focused training aligned with industry demand and high salary careers.\nStudents can choose:\n MBA in Marketing\n MBA in Finance\n MBA in Human Resource (HR)\n MBA in Business Analytics\n MBA in Hospital Management\n MBA in AI & Data Science\nThis makes IAER ideal for students searching for:\n MBA in business analytics Kolkata\n MBA in hospital management Kolkata\n best MBA specialization for high salary\n\nPractical Learning & Corporate Skill Development\nThe programme focuses on real-world exposure to prepare students for corporate jobs after MBA.\nStudents gain hands-on experience through:\n Live Projects & Industry Assignments\n Case Studies & Business Simulations\n Leadership & Team Management Training\n Communication & Presentation Skills\nThis ensures students are job-ready for high salary MBA jobs in India and multinational companies.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned MBA curriculum\n Specialization-based career training\n Practical learning with real-world projects\n Internship opportunities in corporate sectors\n Personality development & leadership training\n Strong industry interaction and expert sessions\n\nInternship Opportunities & Corporate Exposure\nIAER provides structured internships to ensure students gain practical exposure before placement.\nStudents can explore internships with:\n Corporate Companies\n Marketing & Sales Organizations\n Financial Institutions\n Consulting Firms\n Startups & Enterprises\nInternship Roles Include:\n Business Analyst Intern\n Marketing Intern\n Financial Analyst Intern\n HR Intern\n Operations Intern\nThis makes IAER one of the MBA colleges in Kolkata with internship and placement support.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in leading companies across industries.\nStudents are trained through:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Mock Interviews & Corporate Training\n Industry Networking & Placement Drives\n Career Mentorship\n\nGraduates can explore some of the best MBA jobs in Kolkata, including:\n\nCorporate Careers:\n Business Analyst\n Marketing Manager\n Financial Analyst\n HR Manager\n\nManagement Roles:\n Management Trainee\n Operations Manager\n Sales Manager\n\nHigh Growth Roles:\n Business Development Manager\n Entrepreneur / Startup Founder\n\nWhy MBA is the Best Career Option After Graduation\nMBA is one of the most popular postgraduate degrees for career growth, leadership roles, and high salary opportunities.\nStudents searching for:\n best MBA for high salary\n job oriented MBA course Kolkata\n MBA colleges with placement in Kolkata\nchoose IAER for its industry-focused approach and career outcomes.\nGraduates can build careers in:\n Corporate Companies\n Banking & Financial Sector\n Consulting Firms\n E-commerce & Startups\n Healthcare & Analytics Industries\n\nCompare Before You Choose – IAER vs Other MBA Colleges in Kolkata\nStudents often compare:\n EIILM\n BIBS\n UEM\n TECHNO\n GLOBSYN\n PRAXIS\n CBS\nWhile comparing MBA colleges in Kolkata for placement, fees, and ROI, IAER stands out for:\n✔ Affordable fee structure\n✔ Career-oriented training\n✔ Strong placement assistance\n✔ Industry exposure\n\nAffordable MBA Programme in Kolkata with Scholarship & EMI Options\nDesigned for students looking for a low cost MBA college in Kolkata with placement.\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is MBA?\nMBA (Master of Business Administration) is a postgraduate degree focused on business management, leadership, and corporate skills.\n\nWhich is the best MBA college in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best MBA colleges in Kolkata, offering strong placement support and industry-oriented training.\n\nCan I do MBA without entrance exam in Kolkata?\nYes, IAER offers MBA admission without entrance exam in Kolkata based on eligibility and selection process.\n\nWhat are the best MBA jobs in Kolkata?\nTop roles include business analyst, marketing manager, HR manager, and operations manager.\n\nWhat is the MBA course fees in Kolkata?\nMBA fees vary across colleges, but IAER offers an affordable MBA course in Kolkata with scholarship options.\n\nEnquire Now – MBA Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nScholarship & EMI Options Available\nStart Your Corporate Career with MBA\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
