    description: "The Advanced Certification in Airline Cabin Crew at IAER Kolkata is a specialized programme designed for students who want to build careers as air hostesses, flight stewards, and airline cabin crew professionals.",
    longDescription: "Programme Duration\n6 Months Certification Programme\n\nEligibility Criteria\n 10+2 Pass (Any Stream) from a recognized board\n Good communication skills and personality\n Passion for aviation and customer service\n\nProgramme Fee\nTotal Programme Fee: ₹1,00,000. ₹ 60,000\n\nStart Your Career with a Top Cabin Crew Training Institute in Kolkata\nThe Advanced Certification in Airline Cabin Crew at IAER Kolkata is a specialized programme designed for students who want to build careers as air hostesses, flight stewards, and airline cabin crew professionals.\nIAER is emerging as one of the best cabin crew training institutes in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training in aviation service, in-flight operations, and passenger handling. Students searching for:\n cabin crew training in Kolkata\n air hostess training course after 12th\n aviation certification course with placement\nwill find this programme highly aligned with airline industry requirements.\nAffordable Certification Programme with Flexible Payment Options.\nIdeal for students looking for a low cost cabin crew training course in Kolkata.\n\nProfessional Airline Cabin Crew Training\nAs a top air hostess training course in Kolkata, the programme focuses on developing the skills required for airline cabin crew roles.\nStudents are trained in:\n In-Flight Service & Cabin Operations\n Passenger Handling & Safety Procedures\n Emergency & Safety Training\n Grooming & Personality Development\n Communication & Soft Skills\n Aviation Etiquette & Customer Experience\nThis programme is ideal for students looking for:\n air hostess training institute in Kolkata\n cabin crew course after 12th\n aviation training for airline jobs\n\nGrooming, Personality & Communication Training\nIAER provides specialized grooming and personality development sessions to prepare students for airline interviews.\nTraining includes:\n Professional Grooming & Styling\n Communication & Accent Training\n Confidence Building & Interview Skills\n Body Language & Presentation\nThis ensures students meet airline standards for cabin crew and air hostess roles.\n\nProgramme Highlights\n Industry-aligned cabin crew training curriculum\n Focus on airline service and safety procedures\n Practical training through simulations\n Personality development and grooming sessions\n Short duration with quick job opportunities\n Career-oriented training with placement support\n\nInternship & Industry Exposure\nIAER provides exposure to real-world aviation environments through training and industry interaction.\nStudents gain experience through:\n Airline & Airport Exposure Sessions\n Practical Training Simulations\n Customer Service Scenarios\nThis prepares students for airline cabin crew careers in India and abroad.\n\n100% Placement Assistance & Airline Career Opportunities\nIAER offers dedicated placement assistance to all students, helping them secure roles in airlines and aviation service companies.\nStudents receive:\n Resume Building & Interview Preparation\n Grooming for Airline Interviews\n Mock Interviews & Personality Assessment\n Career Guidance & Mentoring\nGraduates can explore some of the best cabin crew jobs in Kolkata and India.\n\nAirline Careers:\n Cabin Crew (Air Hostess / Flight Steward)\n Airline Customer Service Executive\n Ground Staff\n\nAviation & Service Roles:\n Airport Customer Service Executive\n Passenger Handling Executive\n Hospitality & Luxury Service Roles\n\nCareer Scope in Aviation & Airline Industry\nThe aviation industry is growing rapidly, creating strong demand for trained cabin crew professionals.\nStudents completing this cabin crew certification course in Kolkata can build careers in:\n Domestic & International Airlines\n Airport Services & Ground Handling\n Hospitality & Luxury Service Industry\n\nFrequently Asked Questions (FAQs)\n\nWhat is cabin crew training?\nCabin crew training prepares students for roles as air hostesses and flight stewards, focusing on safety, service, and passenger handling.\n\nWhich is the best cabin crew training institute in Kolkata?\nIAER is among the best cabin crew training institutes in Kolkata, offering industry-oriented training and placement support.\n\nIs air hostess a good career option?\nYes, it offers exciting career opportunities, travel exposure, and attractive salary packages.\n\nWhat are the eligibility criteria for cabin crew?\nStudents must complete 10+2 and have good communication skills and personality.\n\nHow to become an air hostess after 12th?\nYou can enroll in a cabin crew training course like this certification programme at IAER Kolkata.\n\nEnquire Now – Cabin Crew Certification Admission Open 2026\nLimited Seats Available\nAffordable Fees\nStart Your Airline Career\nEnquire Now | Book Your Seat | Get Free Counselling",
